<h2 class="sectionedit1"><a name="isfinite" id="isfinite">isfinite</a></h2>
<div class="level2">
<pre class="cpp code cpp"><span class="co2">#include &lt;cmath&gt;</span>
&nbsp;
<span class="kw4">int</span> isfinite<span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">float</span> arg <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span>
<span class="kw4">int</span> isfinite<span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">double</span> arg <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span>
<span class="kw4">int</span> isfinite<span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">long</span> <span class="kw4">double</span> arg <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span></pre><div class="table sectionedit2"><table class="inline">
	<tr class="row0">
		<td class="col0"><a href="../../c_0x" class="wikilink1" title="c_0x">C++0x</a> feature</td>
	</tr>
</table></div>
<!-- EDIT2 TABLE [147-167] -->
<p>

Determines if the given floating point number <code>arg</code> has finite value i.e. it is normal, subnormal or zero, but not infinite or NAN.
</p>

</div>
<!-- EDIT1 SECTION "isfinite" [1-303] -->
<h3 class="sectionedit3"><a name="parameters" id="parameters">Parameters</a></h3>
<div class="level3">

<p>

<code>arg</code> - floating point value
</p>

</div>
<!-- EDIT3 SECTION "Parameters" [304-355] -->
<h3 class="sectionedit4"><a name="return_value" id="return_value">Return value</a></h3>
<div class="level3">

<p>

nonzero value if <code>arg</code> has finite value, zero otherwise
</p>

</div>
